    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great value with this reliable ride! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone needing dependable transportation on a budget. It\u2019s a well-loved vehicle that still has plenty of life left for its next owner to enjoy!",
